                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>reading for children, in the<lb/>\n                <placeName>Philad</placeName> Sunday school, little <sic>stroy</sic><lb/> books for\n                home reading? I think<lb/> they would be needed, something to induce<lb/> a\n                continued attention even in little children<lb/> Those Occidents have not arrived\n                yet.<lb/> Father &amp; Mother join in sending best<lb/> wishes to you</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(9)\">truly yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Amelia E. Ulman</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
